data.meta_description: Enexor BioEnergy | Our mission is to create renewable onsite bioenergy from organic waste to power facilities worldwide.

Team Enexor

We have put together a team of outstanding professionals who are dedicated to being part of a business that is not only successful â€“ but also one that is making a difference in the world. We are passionate about our mission, we challenge each other to improve daily, we work hard and we love to celebrate our success.

Together, we are building great things that make a positive impact on our world and society.

Our home and manufacturing facility.

Our global headquarters and 40,000 sq. ft. manufacturing facility is located in Franklin, Tennessee, a small town next to Nashville. Tennessee is ranked amongst the fastest growing states in the U.S. and is one of the country's most business-friendly states.
